    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "Maps that will make you realize", 
            "dur": "2.418", 
            "start": "1.975"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you know nothing about the Earth.", 
            "dur": "3.063", 
            "start": "4.393"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the world, according\nto the Mercator map projection.", 
            "dur": "3.932", 
            "start": "7.513"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You see this map everywhere,", 
            "dur": "1.646", 
            "start": "11.445"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but did you know that it&#39;s a total lie?!", 
            "dur": "4.465", 
            "start": "13.091"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because the Earth is a sphere,", 
            "dur": "1.698", 
            "start": "18.678"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there is no way to show it\nperfectly on a flat map.", 
            "dur": "2.632", 
            "start": "20.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, all maps are distorted.", 
            "dur": "3.368", 
            "start": "23.008"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here is how countries actually compare.", 
            "dur": "3.55", 
            "start": "27.031"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You might think North America", 
            "dur": "1.119", 
            "start": "31.582"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "looking like nothing compared to Russia,", 
            "dur": "1.463", 
            "start": "32.701"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but in reality Russia is only about", 
            "dur": "1.161", 
            "start": "34.164"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "2.1 times larger than the continental US.", 
            "dur": "3.117", 
            "start": "35.325"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Canada here is all wrong.", 
            "dur": "3.713", 
            "start": "42.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First of all, it&#39;s way too big.", 
            "dur": "2.348", 
            "start": "46.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Canada is actually only about\n1.2 times the size of the US.", 
            "dur": "4.237", 
            "start": "48.698"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Secondly, Canada is shaped more like this.", 
            "dur": "4.59", 
            "start": "52.935"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The United States vs Canada.", 
            "dur": "2.57", 
            "start": "58.075"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What?", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "60.645"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The UK actually looks like this", 
            "dur": "2.804", 
            "start": "69.568"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and Madagascar actually\nlooks more like this.", 
            "dur": "4.607", 
            "start": "72.372"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And here&#39;s what they look like", 
            "dur": "1.808", 
            "start": "79.503"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "compared to the United States.", 
            "dur": "4.059", 
            "start": "81.311"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Greenland and Africa look\nroughly the same size,", 
            "dur": "3.353", 
            "start": "87.487"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "but in reality this is how they compare.", 
            "dur": "2.977", 
            "start": "90.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Africa is almost 14 times larger.", 
            "dur": "3.989", 
            "start": "93.817"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, Africa is larger\nthan a lot of places.", 
            "dur": "3.246", 
            "start": "98.644"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know that huge sheet of\nice at the bottom of the map?", 
            "dur": "3.352", 
            "start": "111.098"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, that is Antarctica\nand it looks like this.", 
            "dur": "3.77", 
            "start": "114.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And compared to Africa,\nit looks like this.", 
            "dur": "5", 
            "start": "118.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Never trust a map.", 
            "dur": "3.957", 
            "start": "127.04"
        }, 
        {
